title: 261: Do We Believe In Ghosts? | Ear Biscuits Ep.261
description:
Have we ever seen a ghost? Do we believe friends who have? It’s all fun and games and beavers until someone sees a dark angel crouching in a fireplace. Listen to R&L discuss a number of true scary stories, including a horrific experience of one Mythical crew member, and their insight into the supernatural on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
